{"tid":2253724,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"京東方傳年底開始供貨蘋果 iPhone 12 / 12 mini 螢幕","createTime":"2020-10-22T10:51:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-25T11:58:34.000Z","uid":134437,"like":4,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"6c9d2a22dd96da86753ef8368e43056e7f4ce55d","tid":2253724,"uid":134437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T10:51:01.000Z","msg":"京東方傳年底開始供貨蘋果 iPhone 12 / 12 mini 螢幕<br />\n<br />\nIT 之家引用「Wise 財經」報導，據產業鏈知情人士透露，中國京東方將於今年底開始供<br />\n貨蘋果新款 iPhone 螢幕。<br />\n<br />\n但京東方供貨範圍僅限 iPhone 12 和 iPhone 12 mini，旗艦款 iPhone 12 Pro 和<br />\niPhone 12 Pro Max 仍由 LG 和三星供應。目前為 iPhone 12 系列供貨的廠商為 LG 和<br />\n三星。在此之前，iPhone X 是京東方首次為蘋果提供 OLED 螢幕的機型，目前京東方在<br />\n成都和綿陽分別有一條第 6 代柔性 AMOLED 生產線。<br />\n<br />\n據消息指出，京東方綿陽 B11 廠於去年投產，良率較低，僅達 20%；成都 B7 廠產品線<br />\n良率則達 70%~80%，主要為<span class=\"red\">華為</span>等中國國產手機供貨。"},{"pid":"2554ef8fbe9511fa3d22412a0b39327c34a73b27","tid":2253724,"uid":134437,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T10:52:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />京東方終國際<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bdeef40b230df5ccefad462cb6801fbfebdbf6f","tid":2253724,"uid":134437,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T10:54:40.000Z","msg":"京東方要晉升頂級螢幕廠商之列了！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6f001dea6760e05e46dd2b48710fdacf34ac5cf","tid":2253724,"uid":39733,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T10:57:07.000Z","msg":"要買趁早"},{"pid":"cc55e9af61240c51202fc6931ba66b40c8e41ef8","tid":2253724,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b6f001dea6760e05e46dd2b48710fdacf34ac5cf","tid":2253724,"uid":39733,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T10:57:07.000Z","msg":"要買趁早"}